Add the /novashell/bin/ to your path. Use export(bash.sh.ksh) or setenv (tcsh,csh). For example:
	$ export PATH=/<my-path-to-novashell>/novashell/bin:$PATH
Try the following command, to get a list of Pig commands:
	$ pig -help

Point $NOVASHELL_CONF_DIR to the directory that contains the nova-conf.xml file. For example:
	$ export NOVASHELL_CONF_DIR=/yournovashellpath/conf/

